	d
	C

FIRST SETS:

first sets of S :
a

first sets of A :
a

first sets of C :
b

first sets of C' :
c ; ε

first sets of X :
a ; b ; d

first sets of Y :
b ; d

FOLLOW SETS:

follow sets of S :
$

follow sets of A :
$

follow sets of C :
$

follow sets of C' :
$

